{
  "texts": [
    "However, the challenge lies in determining the ideal prompt in the era of large language models.",
    "Currently, prompts can be manually created or automatically generated.",
    "While automatically generated prompts may excel in certain tasks, they often lack human readability and explainability.",
    "Thus, in domains where interpretability is paramount, such as in education and research, manual prompt generation may be preferable.",
    "In this study, we develop a series of prompts and chainof-thought prompts, informed by our expertise and cooperated with GPTs develop kit provided ChatGPT website."
  ]
}